{"tid":456994,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好容易覺得孤獨？","createTime":"2017-11-03T12:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T12:38:26.000Z","uid":119450,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e068538a248495b250ca463ac3a0d2dad90307","tid":456994,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"我孤獨有三個原因：<br />\n<br />\n第一係人越大，大家都發展成獨立個體後，人夾人變得越黎越難<br />\n<br />\n第二係亞洲人保守性格，見識好多人識人好謹慎，識個朋友都要諗過度過<br />\n<br />\n但數到底，其實最大原因都係自己性格文靜少野講，好多時候都係欲言又止<br />\n<br />\n媽，我好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140be0a29636efe1e3cd599566a22151f79dd785","tid":456994,"uid":7090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"第2點好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e52d2e1b189892e2d2e396249a6a65b6768435e","tid":456994,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"開始覺得無野"},{"pid":"ce16ff33a01a523b19908d8981068317acc2d6e6","tid":456994,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"都廿中啦，唔孤獨得我跳左樓"},{"pid":"2b7a21201f9202fb44493798d5023c82a3865883","tid":456994,"uid":99001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我孤獨有三個原因：<br />\n<br />\n第一係人越大，大家都發展成獨立個體後，人夾人變得越黎越難<br />\n<br />\n第二係亞洲人保守性格，見識好多人識人好謹慎，識個朋友都要諗過度過<br />\n<br />\n但數到底，其實最大原因都係自己性格文靜少野講，好多時候都係欲言又止<br />\n<br />\n媽，我好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係覺得孤獨<br />\n而係自己根本冇人冇物  死左都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}